headline: Stocks to Watch Recap: U.S. Steel, Kraft Heinz, Circle, Warner Bros.
summary: ↗️ U.S. Steel (X): Japan's Nippon Steel (JP:5401) is set to complete its purchase of U.S. Steel after reaching a national-security agreement with the White House. Shares of the U.S. company jumped 5.1%.
